          "type": "qa",
          "settings": {
            "tab": "1",
            "question": "<p>Event Period</p>",
            "answer": "<p>This promotion is valid from <strong>May 15 to May 26, 2026 (ET)</strong>.<br/><br/>The offer is available exclusively to customers in eligible regions within the <strong>United States</strong>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "qa_7qWXng": {
          "type": "qa",
          "settings": {
            "tab": "1",
            "question": "<p>Promotion Details</p>",
            "answer": "<p>Instant discounts are applied directly to selected Yarbo robots, bundles, and modules during the campaign period. Final pricing and eligible savings are displayed on the corresponding product pages at checkout.<br/><strong><br/>Robots (Include Yarbo Core)</strong><br/>The following robot configurations include the Yarbo Core system:</p><ul><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower — Save <strong>$800 USD</strong></li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower Pro — Save <strong>$400 USD</strong></li></ul><p><strong><br/>Bundles (Include Yarbo Core)<br/></strong>Selected bundle configurations are eligible for promotional savings:</p><ul><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower + Snow Blower + Blower: Save <strong>$1,000 USD</strong></li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower + Snow Blower: Save <strong>$1,000 USD</strong></li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower + Blower: Save <strong>$1,000 USD</strong></li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower Pro + Snow Blower + Blower: Save <strong>$500 USD</strong></li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower Pro + Snow Blower : Save <strong>$500 USD</strong></li><li>Yarbo Lawn Mower Pro + Blower : Save <strong>$500 USD</strong></li></ul><p>Other bundle combinations may not qualify for this promotion.<br/><br/><strong>Individual Modules<br/></strong>Selected standalone modules are also eligible for direct savings:</p><ul><li>Lawn Mower Module: Save <strong>$300 USD</strong></li><li>Lawn Mower Pro Module: Save <strong>$200 USD</strong></li></ul><p><strong><br/>Additional Information<br/></strong>Additional coupons or promotional offers may apply to selected products, subject to checkout eligibility and promotional rules. Final eligibility, availability, and savings are subject to the information displayed on the product page at checkout. <br/></p><p>All promotional items are subject to inventory availability. Yarbo reserves the right to modify or terminate this promotion at any time without prior notice.</p>"
          }
        },
        "tab_dfzie4": {
          "type": "tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "label": "COVERAGE & ELIGIBILITY"
          }
        },
        "qa_cHDQXH": {
          "type": "qa",
          "settings": {
            "tab": "2",
            "question": "<p>Refunds & Returns</p>",
            "answer": "<ul><li>Yarbo offers a <strong>30-day return window</strong> starting from the earlier of either product activation or three days after delivery.</li><li>Items must be returned in <strong>original packaging</strong>, with all accessories included, and in <strong>resalable condition</strong>.</li><li>Missing packaging or accessories may result in a <strong>deduction from the refund</strong>.</li><li>For more details, please refer to the official return policy on the Yarbo website.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
